17,17,17,24,17,17,-9,57,43,22,22,49,45,45,67,64,64,68,61]} 1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6
3. Nc3 Bb4 4. e3 O-O 5. Bd3 c5 6. a3 Bxc3+ 7. bxc3 d6 {Similar to 7...Nc6 8.
Rb1 d6, Black declares his intention to block his opponent's e-pawn and close
