developing dangerous play, based on the pin.} h6 12. Bh4 g5 {A sad necessity -
Black has nothing better than drastically weakening the king.} 13. Bg3 e5 14. f4
$1 {This position took place in a couple of games, including Sarana - Fedoseev,
chess.com 2022. Black's main issue is that the piece is untouchable :} exf4 15.
Nxf4 gxf4 16. Bh4 $18 {with a crushing attack.}) 9. Ng3 $1 {White activates
his knight and at the same time takes control of the important e4 square.} ({
Less precise is} 9. O-O e4 10. Bc2 Be6 $1 $132 {Black is able to keep the
