Black bases his counter-play on active piece play.} 12. Ne2 Bg4 $1 {This is
certainly the most challenging move for White - all Black's minor pieces are
participating now, and 13. ..Nxc3 is threatened.} ({Weaker is} 12... f6 $6 13.
f3 fxe5 ({After} 13... Ng5 14. Bxg5 fxg5 15. O-O {White is much better due to
